    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to arri to nemitteja-\nmu Dedsamo-Uppuri/ un to jau-\nnu Mehneschn/ un wiſſu eezeltu\nSwehtku Uppurus ta KUNga/\nkas twehtiti bija/ lihds ar ikkatru\nlabprahtigu Dahwanu / ko kas\nar labbu Prahtu tam KUNGam\nuppureja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No pirmag Deenas ta sep-\ntita Mehnes eefahze tee tam\nKUNGAM Dedsamo-Uppurus\nuppureht/ tomehr ta Grunte ta\nKUNGA Namma wehl ne bi-\nja likta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad dewe tee teem Zirte-\njeem un Amnata Wihreem\nNaudu/ ir ehst un dsert/ un Et-\nji preekſch teem Zihdonexeem/ un\npreekſch teem no Tirus/ ka tee\nZeedra-Kohkus no ta Lihbanus\nwestu Juhrmalli us Jawu/ ittin\nka Kores tas Persexu Rehninsch\nteein bij wehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu ohtrā Gaddā pehz\nwinzu Atnahfchanas pee ta\nDeewa Namma uis Jerusalemi/\nohtrā Mehnefi/ eefahze Seruba-\nbels Sealtiēta Dehls / un Jesu-\nus Jozadaka Dehls/ un tee At-\nlikuichee no winao Brahteem /\ntee Preesteri un tee Lewitt / un\nwiſſi/ kas no Zeetuma uhs Jeru-\nsalemi bij nahkuichi / un eezeble\ntohs Lewitus no diwidesmits\nGaddeem un pahri/ ka teem bij\nnsraudsiht us to Darbu ta KUN-\nGA Namma.\n"
